CHICAGO, Aug. 11 (AP)--The National Open champion, Dick Mayer, today shook off the lastround jitters that pestered the leaders to fire a 35, 33--68 for a 279 total and win the $50,000 first prize of the "world" golf championship. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
